<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Flaire - Coming Soon...</title>
	<!-- Link to CSS -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
	<!-- Compiled and minified CSS -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.97.7/css/materialize.min.css">
	<!-- Let browser know website is optimized for mobile-->
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
	<!-- Material Icons -->
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
	<!-- Fonts -->
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Josefin+Sans:400,700" rel="stylesheet">
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Domine" rel="stylesheet">
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Signika" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

	<!--  Header w/ Logo & Stuff -->
	<h1 class="center red-text">Flaire</h1>	

	<section class="heading">

		<div id="picture-align" class="valign-wrapper dark-overlay">		
			<div id="heading-text" class="title-text">
				<h5 class="header col s12 title slogan valign">Beauty services and clients at your finger tips!</h5>
				<p class="col s12 slogan valign">
					Flaire connects beauty professionals to clients seeking services near by. Sign up for official release!
				</p>
			</div>			
			
			<div class="form-section col s12 m6" id="desktop-only">
				<form method="POST" action="/thankyou">
					<input type="text" name="name" id="name" required="required">
					<label for="name">Full Name</label>
					<input type="email" name="email" id="email" required>
					<label for="email">E-Mail</label><br><br>
					<label for="comments">Are you a beauty professional?<span style="padding-left:10px;"></span></label>
					<input type="checkbox" name="professional" id="checkbox_id" value="value">
					<label for="checkbox_id"><b>Yes</b></label><br>
					<button style="margin-top:20px;" class="btn waves-effect waves-light" type="submit" name="action">Submit
						<i class="material-icons right">send</i>
					</button>
				</form>
			</div>

		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="heading" id="mobile-only">	
			<div class="form-section">
				<form method="POST" action="/thankyou">
					<input style="color:black;" type="text" name="name" id="name" required="required">
					<label for="name">Full Name</label>
					<input style="color:black;" type="email" name="email" id="email" required>
					<label for="email">E-Mail</label><br><br>
					<label for="yes">Are you a beauty professional?<span style="padding-left:10px;"></span></label>
					<input style="opacity:initial;left:initial;" type="checkbox" id="yes" name="yes" value="true"><br>
					<button style="margin-top:25px;" class="btn waves-effect waves-light" type="submit" name="action">Submit
						<i class="material-icons right">send</i>
					</button>
				</form>
			</div>

		</div>
	</section>

	<!--   Icon Section   -->
	<section class="details container">
		<h5 class="center subtitle">How it works</h5>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col s12 m4 item">
				<div class="icon-block">					
					<h2 class="center light-blue-text"><span>~1~</span></h2>
					<h5 class="center">Search services and professionals</h5>

					<p class="light">- Clients can search for professional beauty services in their areas<br>
					- Professionals can provide a variety of services and showcase their work in their portfolio</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col s12 m4 item">
				<div class="icon-block">
					<h2 class="center light-blue-text"><span>~2~</span></h2>
					<h5 class="center">Choose the date and time</h5>

					<p class="light">- Select a time that works for you at home or at a salon and Flaire will provide a safe and secure booking process<br>
					- Professionals can easily manage payment and scheduling via Flaire</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col s12 m4 item">
				<div class="icon-block">
					<h2 class="center light-blue-text"><span>~3~</span></h2>
					<h5 class="center">Flaire will do the rest!</h5>

					<p class="light">- Enjoy the service at your desired time and leave a review of your experience<br>
					- Professionals can get recommendations and can showcase thier services on clients via social media</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

</body>
</html>